title.english: [Ame no Machi] When I went to a bar alone, an old lady I knew was sitting next to me, and if I pretended not to notice, I would be seduced and have raw sex all night long. [English]
title.japanese: [雨の町] 一人でバーに寄ったら顔見知りのおばさんが隣の席に、、気付かないフリでいるとまさか誘惑されて一晩中生セックスしちゃう漫画 [英語]
title.display: When I went to a bar alone, an old lady I knew was sitting next to me, and if I pretended not to notice, I would be seduced and have raw sex all night long.
